==English==

===Noun===
'''convulsion'''  (''plural:'' '''[[convulsions]]''')
# An intense, [[paroxysmal]], involuntary muscular contraction.
# An uncontrolled fit, as of laughter; a [[paroxysm]].
# Violent turmoil.

